{"tid":2033704,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"突發！美國可能大大力制裁埋香港","createTime":"2020-05-24T21:48:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T23:25:54.000Z","uid":186543,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f7b747b3eac679c89f3a55e0dbfae0636a1332ef","tid":2033704,"uid":186543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T21:48:18.000Z","msg":"美國國家安全顧問奧布萊恩說，北京的做法可能引致美國制裁，亦威脅香港作為金融中心的地位。他說藉著這條國安法例，北京似乎將會基本上接管香港，假如北京方面這樣做，美國國務卿蓬佩奧很可能無法證明香港維持高度自治。奧布萊恩說如果出現這個情況，美方會針對香港及中國，實施制裁措施。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1528104-20200525.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1528104-20200525.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=1ElP8QZN%2FBtuydBCWvxAMjIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=4825e905\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1528104-20200525.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=0c85a469\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1528104-20200525.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n攬炒成功？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aefb3daeabadd6e734651c9579a01d5030c03e08","tid":2033704,"uid":127447,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T21:50:00.000Z","msg":"快啦，做嘢唔洗講咁多。"},{"pid":"f67312e6bdf72549e68cee1c0a919055bc2b54da","tid":2033704,"uid":134571,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T21:51:25.000Z","msg":"正視聽, 係制裁香港政府, 唔係香港"},{"pid":"d30e8d1c9e1f11cc2bf86ef124785b173b7a31a3","tid":2033704,"uid":162268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f67312e6bdf72549e68cee1c0a919055bc2b54da","tid":2033704,"uid":134571,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T21:51:25.000Z","msg":"正視聽, 係制裁香港政府, 唔係香港"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T23:04:42.000Z","msg":"正視聽，係香港人唔願意推返嘅政府"},{"pid":"b159e98e1ddd473621d71d95d1340fe03a6aaaf2","tid":2033704,"u